{"tid":1598183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"代Post 一位2012年10月1日南丫海難家屬","createTime":"2019-09-27T10:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:44:58.000Z","uid":212658,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"67aab2b2f9a9710e99499eedf621b9937f005630","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"敬各位香港人，<br />\n<br />\n當各位因爲「反送中」一事，大家將十月一日的文宣詮釋為「國殤」。<br />\n<br />\n在此，我想提醒大家，今年是「2012年南丫海難」的第七年，希望大家不要忘記事件中不幸離世的39位死者。<br />\n<br />\n或者大家對「南丫海難」一事已經漸漸淡忘，但事實上香港政府仍然欠着39位死者及他們的家屬一個公道。<br />\n<br />\n當日就着「南丫海難」一事而成立的獨立調查委員會已完成調查，但是政府從來沒有將報告公開。到底真相為何，至今仍然是欲蓋彌彰，更沒有任何一個政府官員因此而被問責或承擔任何後果，死者被蒙上不白之冤而家屬欲知事情之前因後果亦是不得要領。<br />\n<br />\n政府護短，大家在最近已經看得一清二楚，而事實上由「南丫海難」一事起，便已是赤裸裸的最佳示範。<br />\n<br />\n或許你們對政府的不滿及失望始於今天，而我對香港政府的痛恨卻是由2012年開始。<br />\n<br />\n今天你們爭取的，我比你們卻是多了一個訴求，但我只是希望你們在爭取訴求的同時，不要忘記「南丫海難」的死者和他們的家屬。<br />\n<br />\n為讓你們能多了解「南丫海難」一事，請你們參考下面維基百科的鏈結或Google搜尋相關新聞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/南丫島撞船事故\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%AB%E5%B3%B6%E6%92%9E%E8%88%B9%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=3c29fc7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/南丫島撞船事故</a><br />\n<br />\n一位南丫海難家屬"},{"pid":"a388ba697fa1c9134ecd938e93501251a2ad0b40","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:14:38.000Z","msg":"希望大家幫推"},{"pid":"a4807fe87e77c94324464f0e666232bb10e3ba84","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:14:49.000Z","msg":"同時 五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"7dc7e6c72f900d0d78d03948d035c01a8456d0c2","tid":1598183,"uid":280136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"同意，不可忘記南丫海難<br />\n<br />\n對抗假新聞假資訊，你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【facebook戰線】大家一齊report曬D垃圾page，等佢地重蹈點新聞嘅覆轍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1596798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1596798</a>"},{"pid":"974104d29a29b7f76b5a7612b10fc2f090d8a530","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"38a7b4b7eaa205f25ef687c3dba76c6c661f4bba","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:15:39.000Z","msg":"幫手推一推丫手足 大家香港人 幫幫自己人"},{"pid":"4885a058176670afc5611a90c5589f2db99f5d11","tid":1598183,"uid":58766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30322cee78af3bfa144ce13ad0f6e71467561a81","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:16:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"78d35c021fc6de92dfbdf4189ac469bbe5f6476c","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:16:26.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"eff74244cf2da9a21bc28bf3cd5cfe2ee61b9054","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:16:42.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"af988a0d81e29b85f533d3715268cff13aa25218","tid":1598183,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:16:52.000Z","msg":"唔公開 極可恥"},{"pid":"05c30f201089d395f602346994ae255cce3ae39b","tid":1598183,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:17:15.000Z","msg":"P牌推空氣都推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b394c2cfa1332a54ca29bde0e731075384a25db","tid":1598183,"uid":266805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"毋忘南丫海難"},{"pid":"6dc13fcfeb1516903f3b14571c9b1e37f5bce22b","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:17:24.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"38a35d50a1ef1fb7ec2908c5971f89048265d83e","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dis