"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:19:33.000Z","msg":"訴"},{"pid":"915d2972bac157f8eab15f721a4b0a2fe0ce552e","tid":1598183,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:19:45.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n我印象中有個政府官好似最後瀨左野<br />\n但我從來唔知道份報告冇公開過<br />\n完成調查唔公開報告？<br />\n咩玩法？<br />\n同時請海難家屬節哀<br />\n我知講咩都唔會令你地唔再傷心難過<br />\n但我地香港人與你地一起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f3b3e4e481cbbf7ca8382800689c6f4ffa9fd9","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:19:46.000Z","msg":"求"},{"pid":"f41cbba1cbda21a4c3ba81a8c0b8be0ccfdfa773","tid":1598183,"uid":79893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:19:46.000Z","msg":"所以你重覺得獨立調查委員會有用?"},{"pid":"f929a35068c4614e1cbdef8fd1fbc407183bbefd","tid":1598183,"uid":288197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"其實從來冇忘記過<br />\n每年一到10.1都提自己咪撚再睇煙花<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10.1港殤</span></span>"},{"pid":"fec4902fc8f78f3fe13ac5c386b672abcaa2658c","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd87cc0ade8fefbbd878ef2630ec5f0766a16f25","tid":1598183,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:23:18.000Z","msg":"幫推一下"},{"pid":"64c3340f4ec2482d1b55d7b87e966e2f37669628","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:23:35.000Z","msg":"各位繼續幫推 ！！"},{"pid":"238e31f0225a68e1af3947fb53a02a6c62dbda98","tid":1598183,"uid":212658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:24:25.000Z","msg":"推車咁推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf10dca93cc3b0c8b3d11264920c